### Error Flow

```
Error Thrown
    ↓
Caught in Controller (try-catch)
    ↓
Passed to next(error)
    ↓
Global Error Handler Middleware
    ↓
Formatted Error Response
    ↓
HTTP Response (4xx/5xx)
```

